{"tid":1496851,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"少女「拿初夜」換EXO門票　網哭「為劉德華」後悔給男友","createTime":"2019-08-22T16:48:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-22T18:17:46.000Z","uid":213300,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b86ac04f69a8e24b5b0ee4eb37835aecdc1f9fd0","tid":1496851,"uid":213300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T16:48:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.nownews.com/news/20190822/3584328/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nownews.com%2Fnews%2F20190822%2F3584328%2F&d=eywEaFxHh3WcM61vPhP2LW0Q%2Fwx8zutUsTDhO6XOofs%3D&h=71b0810b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nownews.com/news/20190822/3584328/</a><br />\n許多日韓星除了在國內舉辦演唱會、見面會，也會定期到海外見粉絲，而台灣正是他們亞<br />\n洲巡迴行程中「必定造訪」的國家，但年紀輕的歌迷因沒有固定收入，導致無足夠的錢購<br />\n票支持偶像，近日就發現有人在臉書求票，卻是要以「初夜」換取，扭曲的價值觀讓眾人<br />\n搖頭。<br />\n<br />\n南韓夯團EXO將於9月28、29日一連兩天在台北小巨蛋開唱，2場演出開賣即秒殺，一名網<br />\n友就在「爆怨公社」表示，看到有女歌迷在網路求EXO的票，但卻被條件嚇到，原來對方<br />\n想用初夜換取2張搖滾區位置，無奈詢問大家：「是不是我老了，跟不上現代社會的價值<br />\n觀了？」不敢相信真的有人為了見偶像而願意出賣身體。<br />\n<br />\n該貼文立即得到迴響，不少人見怪不怪，更表示不只演唱會門票，還曾看過有人為了其他<br />\n物品賣身，也有網友自嘲，笑說：「初夜可以換劉德華的門票，我當初不該給另一半的！<br />\n」相當諷刺。"},{"pid":"6acaec42e7269abf2415e871bf09a651741cd6ed","tid":1496851,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T16:49:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcSt0Kk7uslYTceOQusGf9Nj8G8Xy7PhTNimPyuOq5EvD7gmyFnpcA\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fencrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com%2Fimages%3Fq%3Dtbn%3AANd9GcSt0Kk7uslYTceOQusGf9Nj8G8Xy7PhTNimPyuOq5EvD7gmyFnpcA&h=8879c153&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c9fb178429fa29db3440d6f88569518a4146b6b5","tid":1496851,"uid":251836,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T16:50:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4DMhPEO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4DMhPEO.jpg&h=03875568&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1acd65e20c885bf1123978dc042dba24782b8457